Juventus lost 2-1 to Torino in the Serie A derby on Sunday . 
  Andrea Pirlo scored a stunning free-kick for Juventus in the first-half . 
  Matteo Darmian and Fabio Quagliarella scored for Torino . 
  Juve could have wrapped up their fourth straight Serie A title . 
  But they fell to a shock defeat at local rivals Torino  . 
 